'''''A Vava Inuva''''' d album yettwasnen n useggas n 1976 n ucennay [[Aqbayli]] [[Yidir]]. deg-s tizlitt yesɛan isem aluman (même) "A Vava Inouva", deg-s diɣen tezlatin nniḍen am "Azwaw", "Zwit Rwit" (laṣṣel n tezlitt "[[El harba wine]]" n [[Khaled (musician)|Xaled]]), "Ssendu" akk-d "Cfiɣ".

== Tezlitt: "A Vava Inuva" ==
"'''A Vava Inuva'''", d tezlitt n wezwel deg welbum. D tezlitt tamezwarutt n [[Tafrikt n Ugafa|Tefriqt Ugafa]] ig wḍen ɣeṛ weswir agraɣlan. Yecna-tt [[Yidir]] d tcennayt Mila.

Tezlitt-ayi tettsuqel ɣeṛ waṭaṣ n tutlayin am [[Tutlayt taɛrabt|teɛrabt]], [[Tutlayt taspenyult|tespenyult]], [[Tafrensist|tefrensist]], [[tagrikit]] d tiyaḍ. [[David Jisse]] akk-d Dominique Marge sufeɣ-n taḍrist [[tafransist]] s yissem ''"Ouvre-moi vite la porte"'' (Ɣiwel ldi-yi-d tawwurt). Acennay agriki [[Katevas]] ysuffeɣ taḍrist tagrikit "An ginotane" (s tegrikit '''''Αν γινότανε''''') akk-d [[Efi Strati]]. [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uynTZT7ML7c Tabidyut] deg [[YouTube]].
